# Sul PC: http://127.0.0.1:3000/it  http://127.0.0.1:7000  http://127.0.0.1:5173  (API :9000)

Host tramelle-forward
    HostName 82.165.134.103
    User root
    LocalForward 127.0.0.1:3000 127.0.0.1:3000
    LocalForward 127.0.0.1:7000 127.0.0.1:7000
    LocalForward 127.0.0.1:9000 127.0.0.1:9000
    LocalForward 127.0.0.1:5173 127.0.0.1:5173
